wiki.summary: “NIGHT RIDER” is the sixth track from Joji’s third studio album SMITHEREENS and is the start of the album's second side. This track is notable for being the only track off of the album to be produced by just Joji himself. The track sees Joji and his lover in a relationship where Joji is always looking for adventure in life but his lover is the complete opposite resulting in Joji being selfish and doing things on his own terms. Read more on Last.fm.
